name: Pro Keds x Norse Projects Royal Master White Smoke $200, Now
description: Norse Projects have taken the classic  silhouette and given it the contemporary treatment, presenting a  stripped down version of the low-cut royal masters in three colourways.  Available in Dark Navy, Light Grey, and Okker Yellow, each colourway  draws its inspiration from prominent elements of everyday life in Norse  Projects’ home town Copenhagen, the ocean, the beach, and the town  itself. Each colourway features a soft pigskin suede upper, co-branded  cork inner sole, premium leather lining, and aniline dyed leather heel  tab.
